# Static assets placeholder

Add the following assets to this directory:

- `favicon.ico` - Browser tab icon (16x16, 32x32)
- `logo.svg` - Site logo (vector format recommended)
- `social-card.png` - Open Graph/Twitter card image (1200x630 recommended)
{%- if docusaurus_pwa == 'enabled' %}
- `icon-192.png` - PWA icon (192x192)
- `icon-512.png` - PWA icon (512x512)
{%- endif %}

## Social Card Tips

Your social card appears when links are shared on Twitter, LinkedIn, Slack, etc.
Recommended dimensions: 1200x630 pixels (1.91:1 aspect ratio)

Create with tools like:
- Canva: https://canva.com
- Figma: https://figma.com
- og:image generator: https://og-playground.vercel.app
{%- endif -%}
